"If Bluetooth settings doesn't appear, your computer might not support Bluetooth. In this case, we recommend you purchase a Bluetooth dongle that supports Bluetooth 4.0 and above, for example <a href=\"http://www.newegg.com/Product/Product.aspx?Item=N82E16833139027\" target=\"_blank\">this one</a>.\n"
